{"type": "article", "id": 37865, "title": "你想过折纸艺术和饭团能组合出什么奇妙的产品么？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-02-16T22:57:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 37710, "name": "向日葵设计"}, {"id": 37711, "name": "Today Is Art Day"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 125, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170216172740jurA0iYZ59VLqDaH.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Orinigiri by 向日葵设计</h3><p>当日本传统的折纸艺术和美味的饭团结合在一起，会诞生怎样的产品呢？为了更好地推广传统文化，日本一间名为<a href=\"http://himawari-design.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">向日葵设计</a>的工作室开发了一套名为 <a href=\"http://orinigiri.com/index.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Orinigiri</a> 的纸质模具，饭团在它们的帮助下可以变身成富士山等八种不同的造型。这些模具曾在东日本大地震后的一系列志愿者活动中，作为工作坊的道具投入使用，供受灾地的孩子们制作饭团。去年，Orinigiri 还因此赢得了日本的<a href=\"https://www.g-mark.org/award/describe/44594\" rel=\"nofollow\">优良设计奖</a>（Good Design）。目前它正在进行<a href=\"https://www.makuake.com/project/orinigiri/\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹</a>，套装的最低价为 1360 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216172826VdYpculZMavJ0KRy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216172826sIHSPFbWXkOQr51e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216172825WveUtdVDHcMNCFuZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216172826KHe2kZocmrnMOlXt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216172825MDs6umax2zC3cZ8w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216172825VqyPXhxvmK0f4Flu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Vincent Van Gogh Action Figure by Today Is Art Day</h3><p>来自加拿大的 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/todayisartday/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Today Is Art Day</a> 是一个致力于用有趣的方式科普艺术知识的社交媒体账号，当运营团队发现艺术类周边产品很少有更具亲和力的玩具模型时，他们决定开发以知名艺术家为形象的手办。这款头大身小的梵高手办就是他们的试水作，可拆卸的双耳和大胡子很忠于人物形象，胸口还别着一枚向日葵胸针。外包装的纸盒上印有数幅梵高的代表作，你还可以把它们连同下方的画框一起裁下来，放在梵高身边。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/todayisartday/vincent-van-gogh-action-figure\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 28 美元。如果筹集到 125000 美元，手办还会增加一个绑着绷带的耳朵配件。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216173106YNpn8sj7PeiCqdJo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702161731067RNEG9W1zLBXTxca.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664615\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216173106Xs9Sy3mG06NvtluT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216173105wlK0ATvy32ZhDitd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216173105rTBnm8uEcL3FC9xl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.629808\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Alia Grace Dolls</h3><p>想舒缓眼部疲劳，冰凉的鱼会是一个好主意吗？美国手工爱好者 Alia Grace 热衷于制作富有幽默感的娃娃，这些软绵绵的鱼形眼枕就是她的最新作品，狭长的造型刚好可以覆盖住双眼。枕头的内部填充了薰衣草和有机亚麻种子，只要进行简单的热敷就能使用。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/AliaGraceDolls\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 36 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216173048bjAFrzuIXks25lKq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.924615\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216173047Z2CaLWf6Dqwz8cuE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750769\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702161730478jqFhuRC1XTkwA6V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.160000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216173048lN24nSCBfYPzFxR5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.816923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Fluid Porcelain by Aylin Bilgiç</h3><p>土耳其手工艺人 <a href=\"http://www.aylinbilgic.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Aylin Bilgiç</a> 擅长制作各类陶瓷制品，最近她尝试将液体飞溅的瞬间定格下来，打造了一批有着流动液体感的瓷碗。当你仔细观察瓷碗的边缘，会发现液体溅出的部分似乎更薄一些，在光线下有些透明。Bilgiç 还在纯白色的瓷碗边缘加入了金色，看起来相当优雅。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216173020GxngziKkAXWcZT7E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216173020ZBsIQog8zptkRx7H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216173020rLeGt9DboHUQRcTg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216173020YVW5rpIm6KTq9LbC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216173020Y7Tlou0wzXKCni1s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>150 Years National Archaeological Museum by Konstantina Vatavali</h3><p>位于希腊雅典的国家考古博物馆于去年迎来了它建馆 150 周年，在雅典技术教育学院（Technological Educational Institute of Athens）就读的平面设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/konstantinavatavali\" rel=\"nofollow\">Konstantina Vatavali</a> 为此重新设计了一组<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/43794431/150-Years-National-Archaeological-Museum\" rel=\"nofollow\">品牌形象</a>。以 150 为主题的数字 logo 是 Vatavali 借鉴博物馆的外观设计的，和外部立柱有些相似。在门票、书签等产品上出现的人物图案分别对应了馆内著名的藏品，Vatavali 只保留了它们的轮廓和颜色，最后再加上寥寥几笔补充细节，变得生动不少。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216172920qnSXl3trKoVdY4yM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.615000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216172919Qy5q04JgCDflcNFj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.615000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216172919MeafntD9S7GqIdRC.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.332500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216172919X0AJEcBbTKsF9who.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.615000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216172920fyW30AboPtijFwdn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216172924wvPVxjIYCX483Tni.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.615000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Desserted in Paris by Tal Spiegel</h3><p>Tal Spiegel 是法国巴黎的一位甜点师，平面设计出身的他在晒吃这件事上发掘出了另一种形式。他拍摄的 Desserted in Paris 系列不仅有精美诱人的甜品，还配有特意挑选的同色系的穿搭。深谙这些照片的种草能力，Spiegel 也会留下甜品店的名字以及衣服的品牌，让人们可以安心地来一场巴黎甜品之旅。你可以在 Spiegel 的 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/desserted_in_paris/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> 账号上浏览全部照片。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216172851whbHVdOutPMX2Cv8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216172850DTIGomHBfxcFJPih.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216172850kZ3Y5pFRgJrxoy9m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216172851AuSMTgaXcrk86vEj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170216172851xbaUEmGki07frACd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}